                    <fixVersion>6.0</fixVersion>
                                        <due></due>
                            <votes>2</votes>
                                    <watches>4</watches>
                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="14185173" author="ehatcher" created="Mon, 27 Oct 2014 14:22:34 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This has historically been a problem, and I&apos;ve always adjusted the example configurations when I build prototypes/demos to have this ${solr.install.dir} system property concept.  Now that we have start scripts, we can simply pass in the already known Solr &quot;install&quot; (under which contrib/ lives, most importantly for this issue) directory. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14185183" author="ehatcher" created="Mon, 27 Oct 2014 14:32:24 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This patch adjusts all example configurations with relative &amp;lt;lib&amp;gt; paths to keep the default, but override with ${solr.install.dir} system property.  The (&apos;nix only!) start script has been adjusted to pass this property in. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14185214" author="anshumg" created="Mon, 27 Oct 2014 14:58:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1 on this! LGTM.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14186270" author="jira-bot" created="Tue, 28 Oct 2014 03:05:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1634770 from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=ehatcher&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;ehatcher&quot;&gt;ehatcher&lt;/a&gt; in branch &apos;dev/trunk&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1634770&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1634770&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-6661&quot; title=&quot;Address relative path &amp;lt;lib&amp;gt; references&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-6661&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-6661&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Adjust all example configurations to allow overriding error-prone relative paths for solrconfig.xml &amp;lt;lib&amp;gt; references with solr.install.dir system property; bin/solr scripts will set it appropriately.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14186271" author="jira-bot" created="Tue, 28 Oct 2014 03:08:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1634771 from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=ehatcher&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;ehatcher&quot;&gt;ehatcher&lt;/a&gt; in branch &apos;dev/branches/branch_5x&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1634771&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1634771&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-6661&quot; title=&quot;Address relative path &amp;lt;lib&amp;gt; references&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-6661&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-6661&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Adjust all example configurations to allow overriding error-prone relative paths for solrconfig.xml &amp;lt;lib&amp;gt; references with solr.install.dir system property; bin/solr scripts will set it appropriately.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14186274" author="ehatcher" created="Tue, 28 Oct 2014 03:10:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Also added this to bin/solr.cmd for Windows as well (someone please test).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14199434" author="ehatcher" created="Thu, 6 Nov 2014 00:14:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Re-opening so this can tackled for a 4.10.3 release as well.  It&apos;s already on 5x and trunk, just not 4x yet&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14207236" author="jira-bot" created="Tue, 11 Nov 2014 22:41:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1638496 from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=ehatcher&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;ehatcher&quot;&gt;ehatcher&lt;/a&gt; in branch &apos;dev/branches/lucene_solr_4_10&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1638496&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1638496&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-6661&quot; title=&quot;Address relative path &amp;lt;lib&amp;gt; references&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-6661&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-6661&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Adjust all example configurations to allow overriding error-prone relative paths for solrconfig.xml &amp;lt;lib&amp;gt; references with solr.install.dir system property; bin/solr scripts will set it appropriately. (merged from branch_5x r1634771, manually fixing solr/CHANGES.txt conflict)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14207270" author="ehatcher" created="Tue, 11 Nov 2014 22:54:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;committed this to the 4.10 branch so it&apos;ll be on releases 4.10.3+&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
